(secondQuint)A Study of the Effect of SYN-010 on Subjects With IBS-C.

 This is a Phase 2, randomized, multi-center, multi-dose study.

 Sixty subjects with irritable bowel syndrome with constipation who are between the ages of 18 and 65, inclusive, will be enrolled.

 The entire duration of the study may be up to 43 days (from Screening to the post end-of-study [EOS] visit telephone call).

